<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />For your sake I have borne rebuke;</para>

<para style="q1">shame has covered my face.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />I have become a stranger to my brothers,</para>

<para style="q1">an alien to my mother's children.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />For the zeal of your house has eaten me up,</para>

<para style="q1">and the rebukes of those who rebuke you have fallen on me.</para>
